These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, car
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | mystery |
| Transport     | car | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, baseball
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | pomegranate      | lettuce         |
| Sport   | climbing | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: lime, zucchini
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice   |
| Food       | zucchini  | lime |

 #################################

 
